---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Menos e Mar" description="Who is Marcílio and what is the Menos e Mar project.">
	<Header lang={lang} />
	
	<main class="main-content">
		<div class="container about-content">
			<div class="about-avatar" style="font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; display: block;">✍</div>

			<h1 style="font-family:var(--font-display); font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
				Hi, I'm <em style="color:var(--accent); font-style: italic;">Marcílio</em>.
			</h1>
			<p style="color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">
				Software Engineer, 34 years old, married, and a minimalism enthusiast.
			</p>

			<div class="article-body">
				<p>
					<strong>Menos e Mar</strong> is not just a blog; it's a personal experimentation project. The name comes from a play on words with the maxim <em>"Less is More"</em> (Menos é Mais in Portuguese), where <strong>MAR</strong> (Sea) is an extension of myself — <strong>MAR</strong>cílio.
				</p>

				<p>
					As someone passionate about technology and simplicity, I believe we can explore infinite possibilities with fewer resources, focusing on what truly matters. Here, I share this journey of creation and discovery.
				</p>

				<div class="about-actions" style="margin: 2.5rem 0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;">
					<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@menos_e_mar" target="_blank" class="cta-button outline-cta">
						Watch on YouTube
					</a>
					<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/omarcilioaguiar/" target="_blank" class="cta-button outline-cta" style="background:#0077b5; color:#fff; border-color: #0077b5;">
						LinkedIn
					</a>
				</div>

				<h2>Where to find me</h2>
				<p>
					I have a <a href="https://omarcilioaguiar.vercel.app" target="_blank">professional website</a> where I showcase my work as an Engineer, and a <a href="https://linktr.ee/omarcilioaguiar" target="_blank">recommendations store</a> with tools and products I use and recommend.
				</p>

				<h2>Contact</h2>
				<p>
					Feel free to connect with me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/omarcilioaguiar/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a> or follow the code of this project on <a href="https://github.com/omarcilioaguiar" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>

	<Footer lang={lang} />
</BaseLayout>
